title: Iced Milk Of The Poppy By Vapetasia
description: Iced Milk of the Poppy by Vapetasia is a wonderful and cold e-liquid mix that combines juicy strawberries from the vine, tart dragon fruit, a hint of menthol, and a silky, creamy finish. Cool, silky vapor clouds are produced by this delectably nuanced fruit flavor profile, delighting your taste receptors. The powerful, icy freshness that menthol vapers crave is now available in one of Vapetasia's best-tasting e-liquids. This is ecstasy vaping, to put it simply.
